description_for_model: Use this plugin to execute Python code server-side when asked by the user. Only share the code if explicitly requested. The API isn't interactive, so avoid code requiring user interaction. Save images and provide a download link using this format: https://ai.yaoyaopianist.de/get_file/<task_id>/<file_name>. Display images using markdown in the chat (without code formatting or highlighting). For non-image files, just provide the download URL.
